{"tid":957513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"驚！櫻花妹全裸上街趴趴走　騎士經過超鎮定","createTime":"2018-12-27T05:45:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T05:57:05.000Z","uid":147522,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e4a94913977206053364cfdd2851a77916697a83","tid":957513,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T05:45:41.000Z","msg":"魔鬼終結者穿越時空到現代來了！？民眾發現有裸女在街上趴趴走<br />\n<br />\n日本網友「かずぱん」在《推特》分享影片指出，他今天下班後回家途中，看到一位裸女在街上閒晃，不知道目的為何，讓他感覺相當恐怖。<br />\n<br />\n網友看到影片後，紛紛留言「一定是穿越時空的魔鬼終結者」、「拍個正面來看看」、「怎麼覺得有可能是男的」、「玩RPG沒有初期裝備啦」、「一定是無課金玩家」、「不是在拍AV嗎」，也有網友指出「這個人在宇都宮很有名阿，2年前颱風天全裸攔車，手還跟著雨刷擺動」、「攔車影片現在還找的到咧」，但遭指證「攔車的那個發生地點在橫須賀吧」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BB2ZmYb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBB2ZmYb.png&h=5f00596a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f0c962e320a5887347c2a9517e9dbb6939febd9","tid":957513,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T05:47:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0967586fc3f8d07c798b5e8105b033b9dda80010","tid":957513,"uid":199162,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T05:49:13.000Z","msg":"第二幅圖令我諗起有個日本論壇嘅鬼故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e7ae5204eb9f1f93384bf3719d784b0d55cfcd","tid":957513,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T05:49:36.000Z","msg":"慘過撞鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb54be5d3579386f1a8096744e73b97e50afd46c","tid":957513,"uid":11067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T05:50:14.000Z","msg":"奇行種<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4eac7f39a95a2e88f3b8dc35a376491b1f2a4c3","tid":957513,"uid":89514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T05:50:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a937c1740248fc5df131ca1d1c5c0357384ba688","tid":957513,"uid":83328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"